use, allows those individuals to say that,

30
00:01:44.514 --> 00:01:47.775
The buttons in my product
all look the same, right?

31
00:01:47.775 --> 00:01:51.857
So there's a level of consistency or
cohesion at that individual level.

32
00:01:51.857 --> 00:01:56.374
And having foundations, tokens in core
systems, those fundamental layers will

33
00:01:56.374 --> 00:02:00.498
allow your departments, like a larger
part of the organization, to say,

34
00:02:00.498 --> 00:02:03.650
