43
00:02:35.906 --> 00:02:38.158
mission and vision of your company.

44
00:02:38.158 --> 00:02:42.276
It's different than consistency at
the individual and department level,

45
00:02:42.276 --> 00:02:46.650
because it speaks to interactions with
your company's audience way beyond just

46
00:02:46.650 --> 00:02:48.272
the digital work that you do.

47
00:02:48.272 --> 00:02:52.764
