50
00:03:00.858 --> 00:03:05.157
And this is a really healthy perspective
I think for us to get back to.

51
00:03:05.157 --> 00:03:09.982
I'm not saying that having a design system
is gonna give you this automatically, but

52
00:03:09.982 --> 00:03:14.270
design systems that start rooted in
the brand and build out are gonna at least

53
00:03:14.270 --> 00:03:17.702
