these layers that really give that to us.

59
00:03:37.629 --> 00:03:43.306
The assets will enable an individual to
design or build a feature faster, right?

60
00:03:43.306 --> 00:03:47.817
I have the things I need to be
able to do the work I wanna do.

61
00:03:47.817 --> 00:03:52.825
And I think the processes allow us to work
more efficiently with each other, right?

62
00:03:52.825 --> 00:03:55.275
That's gonna help us get to market faster.

63
00:03:55.275 --> 00:03:59.128
We're defining how we work as individuals,
