82
00:05:04.349 --> 00:05:08.459
a language for communicating with each
other about the problems we're solving.

83
00:05:08.459 --> 00:05:12.171
That kind of miscommunication
is widespread, and

84
00:05:12.171 --> 00:05:15.634
it creates the most
damaging inefficiencies.

85
00:05:15.634 --> 00:05:20.430
I've talked with folks who've experienced
this, it's frustrating for the employees,

86
00:05:20.430 --> 00:05:22.808
it creates animosity between departments.

87
00:05:22.808 --> 00:05:23.654
And at the root,

